tweet: We are, what we think we are!
Foods rich in Vitamin A preserve and improve your eyesight & help you fight off viral infections!
How do you know if you need more Vitamin A? You experience night blindness or you have frequent viral infections
The foods with the highest concentration of Vitamin A? Carrots by far, then Spinach, and Kale
In addition, Calf's liver and sweet potatoes have a high consecration of Vitamin A, although they are also a lot higher in calories
